{"tid":962176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 開工前稱心口不適　小巴司機猝死車廂","createTime":"2018-12-30T16:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T00:54:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60eb9f700bca67725b5babf1bacfa7be21b79a01","tid":962176,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"寒冷天氣警告下，今日（30日）傍晚6時許，油麻地寧波街25號一小巴站，一輛來往佐敦至藍田的紅頂小巴停車候客，有行家發現年約50歲的男司機在車廂昏迷，慌忙報警求助。救護員接報趕至，替司機急救再送院搶救，惜終告不治，警方正就事件調查。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，事主患有心臟病，接受過「通波仔」手術，今日開工前曾向同事透露心口不適，又曾回家服藥。至開工時並無異樣，其後有行家發現事主良久不動，覺可疑查看始揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181230/bkn-20181230205627443-1230_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181230%2Fbkn-20181230205627443-1230_00822_001.html&d=hm2g6INAMOabbn7Boy1dYVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=4eae959a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181230/bkn-20181230205627443-1230_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a26867d3bfba58b7792119256913cbf73d526221","tid":962176,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181230/photo/bkn-20181230205627443-1230_00822_001_02p.jpg?20181230223034\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181230%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181230205627443-1230_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20181230223034&h=5e38da3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45e50a042cf35ec4cedd0bec2ad601be6f76c6e9","tid":962176,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"咁架巴士算唔算兇巴？<br />\n有冇第二個敢揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7aeced53cf7a65d32e888be33e37272a0dcd0e","tid":962176,"uid":18381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:26:24.000Z","msg":"坐過佢幾次車，佢幾好人<br />\n咁就走左，RIP ..... <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.